# Tutorial — Running & Publishing Generated YTP Videos

This tutorial covers how to preview, process, optimize, subtitle, thumbnail, and publish the chaotic YTP videos generated by WebPoop.js. It includes practical ffmpeg commands and Windows (including Windows 8.1) guidance.

