## Thumbnails & metadata

Create a thumbnail frame (example at 5 seconds):
```
ffmpeg -ss 00:00:05 -i input.mp4 -frames:v 1 -q:v 2 thumbnail.jpg
```
- Use `-ss` before `-i` for fast seek or after `-i` for frame-accurate.

Generate multiple preview thumbnails (every N seconds):
```
ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -vf "select='not(mod(t,5))',scale=1280:-1" -vsync vfr -q:v 2 thumbs_%03d.jpg
```

Add metadata (title, artist) to MP4:
```
ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -metadata title="WebPoop YTP" -metadata artist="Creator" -codec copy output_meta.mp4
```

