## Sharing & hosting

- Large file sharing: use Google Drive, Dropbox, or WeTransfer for sending raw outputs.
- For embeddings on the web, transcode smaller versions (lower resolution/CRF).
- For short clips (TikTok/Reels/Instagram), reformat to vertical (9:16) with cropping/scale and tight duration limits.

Convert for social vertical upload (example center-crop to 9:16):
```
ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -vf "scale=1080:-1, crop=1080:1920" -c:v libx264 -crf 23 -c:a aac -b:a 128k output_vertical.mp4
```

