## Quick reference commands

Re-encode to web-ready MP4:
```
ffmpeg -i in.mp4 -c:v libx264 -preset fast -crf 18 -c:a aac -b:a 192k -movflags +faststart out.mp4
```

Normalize audio:
```
ffmpeg -i in.mp4 -af "loudnorm=I=-16:TP=-1.5:LRA=11" -c:v copy out_norm.mp4
```

Create thumbnail at 5s:
```
ffmpeg -ss 00:00:05 -i in.mp4 -frames:v 1 -q:v 2 thumb.jpg
```

Embed SRT into MP4 (soft subs):
```
ffmpeg -i in.mp4 -i subs.srt -c copy -c:s mov_text out_subs.mp4
```

Burn Impact meme text:
```
ffmpeg -i in.mp4 -vf "drawtext=fontfile='C\\:/Windows/Fonts/impact.ttf':text='MEME':fontsize=72:fontcolor=white:stroke_color=black:stroke_w=3:x=(w-text_w)/2:y=h-(text_h*1.5)" -c:a copy out_meme.mp4
```

Split into 10s segments:
```
ffmpeg -i in.mp4 -c copy -map 0 -f segment -segment_time 10 -reset_timestamps 1 out%03d.mp4
```

