## Legal & safety notes

- Copyright: YTPs commonly reuse copyrighted clips — ensure compliance with copyright law and platform policies. Fair use is context-dependent; if uncertain, avoid publishing copyrighted materials without permission.
- Content warnings: include clear warnings for extreme audio (ear-rape), flashing content (photosensitive seizure risk), or explicit language.
- Respect privacy and avoid creating deepfakes or manipulative content that harms individuals.

